          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 13012,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1301201,
            "DisplayOrder": 250,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 7400,
            "LocalizeKR": "탈출 훈련의 시범입니다!\n불의의 사고로 수갑에\n묶였을 때를 대비하여,",
            "LocalizeJP": "だ、脱出訓練の予行演習です！\n想定外の事態が起きて、\n万が一拘束されてしまった\n時のために……",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 13012,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1301201,
            "DisplayOrder": 260,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 7000,
            "LocalizeKR": "본관이 직접 탈출하는\n시범을 보이겠습니다!",
            "LocalizeJP": "これより本官が、\n脱出の仕方をお見せします！",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 13012,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1301201,
            "DisplayOrder": 270,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 8700,
            "LocalizeKR": "안심하시길! 본관처럼\n제대로 훈련을 받은 경찰이라면,\n이 정도는 간단하니까요!",
            "LocalizeJP": "ご安心ください！\n本官のようにしっかり訓練を\n積んだ者であれば、\nこれくらい簡単ですから！",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_04_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
